SUBJECT: My Dear,
My Dear,
I am looking for a possible tie-up with a business in your country so
that I can do some property investments and any other good investments.
Please reply for further explanation.
Thanks
Fahad Abdus-Sabur
From: a*********f@gmail.com
To: wt14358@m**************m
Time: 2023-03-26 23:05:26
SUBJECT: Dear Tiffany Reply
Dear Tiffany
Thank you for responding to my message I sent to you, I got your contact
from LinkedIn Corporation, let me explain more about the reasons why I
contacted you so that you can understand clearly why I reached out to you.
I am looking at making property investments which I will eventually use in
achieving permanent residency for myself and my family through real estate
investments.
I want to go into a business partnership with you through which the
investments will be made in a joint venture with your production company.
The reason why I need a business partner is that I do not know the local
economy to go into a business by myself.
That is why I want to enter into a partnership with you even though any
investment or business I set up will be funded 100% wholly by me. All I
need from you is your local expertise which will be crucial for any
business I set up or invest that I do to succeed. My investment amount is
US$50,000.000.00.
Looking forward to your response
Regards,
Fahad Abdus-Sabur
From: a*********f@gmail.com
To: wt14358@m**************m
Time: 2023-03-28 08:30:46
SUBJECT: INFORMATION
Dear Tiffany
Thank you for your response to my message, I hope that my email finds you
well. I want to emigrate as an investor in your country so that I can
restart my business life there as well as offer my family the opportunity
of a peaceful living which is no longer available to us here in Syria.
I will highly appreciate good business ideas for an investment fund in your
country as you know more about your country's economy and profitable
projects to invest fund also you can check on the below investment plans,
we should work accordingly and I will give you an explanation when I
confirm your full interest which I will give you all details in the
agreement pages
(1) Residential real estate includes both new constructions and resale
homes.
(2) Livestock Ranching/Pastoral Farming
I will need a business partner that will help me make the investments as I
will like you to direct the best profitable project that you are an expert
to control project is very good and I will like you to handle the fund and
invest in a proper business.
I will need to qualify for the investor immigration visa through a
partnership that we will enter into. The investments will be funded wholly
by me.
What I am seeking is an industrial partner that will handle the
organizational aspect of the investment while I take care of the funding.
It is a big risk to invest in a market where you have no knowledge of the
local market fundamentals. That is why I am seeking a partnership with you
so that you can provide the required local knowledge which is very crucial.
I am going to offer you a Fund Management Fee of 5% and 40% of profits
earned during the duration of the partnership which will be for a minimum
period of five years.
If my offer is acceptable to you please send your address and full name so
that I can prepare a General Business Partnership Agreement with the terms
that I proposed.
Full Name:
Address:
Telephone
Occupation
Once we have signed the agreement I will transfer to you a Business
Start-Up fund of US$50,000.00 to prepare all essential things through which
the property investments will be made.
Looking forward to your response
Regards,
Abdus-Sabur Fahad
